{"id":"penguin-learns-to-slide","slug":"penguin-learns-to-slide","title":"Penguin Learns to Slide","title_ko":"펭귄이 미끄럼을 배워요","level":"A1","ageBand":"8-10","coverUrl":"/seed/penguin-learns-to-slide/cover.webp","summary_ko":"걷기만 하던 아기 펭귄이 친구를 보고 배로 미끄러지는 법을 배우는 이야기예요.","wordCount":90,"pages":[{"id":"penguin-learns-to-slide-p1","pageNo":1,"spread":"p1","imageUrl":"/seed/penguin-learns-to-slide/p1.webp","sentences":[{"id":"penguin-learns-to-slide-p1-s1","ord":0,"text":"Pip is a small penguin.","translation_ko":"핍은 작은 펭귄이에요.","audioUrl":"/seed/penguin-learns-to-slide/audio/p1-s1.mp3","wordTimings":[{"word":"Pip","charStart":0,"charEnd":3,"startMs":0,"endMs":300},{"word":"is","charStart":4,"charEnd":6,"startMs":300,"endMs":500},{"word":"a","charStart":7,"charEnd":8,"startMs":500,"endMs":660},{"word":"small","charStart":9,"charEnd":14,"startMs":660,"endMs":920},{"word":"penguin","charStart":15,"charEnd":22,"startMs":920,"endMs":1240}]},{"id":"penguin-learns-to-slide-p1-s2","ord":1,"text":"He likes the white snow.","translation_ko":"핍은 하얀 눈을 좋아해요.","audioUrl":"/seed/penguin-learns-to-slide/audio/p1-s2.mp3","wordTimings":[{"word":"He","charStart":0,"charEnd":2,"startMs":0,"endMs":620},{"word":"likes","charStart":3,"charEnd":8,"startMs":620,"endMs":1000},{"word":"the","charStart":9,"charEnd":12,"startMs":1000,"endMs":1340},{"word":"white","charStart":13,"charEnd":18,"startMs":1340,"endMs":1680},{"word":"snow","charStart":19,"charEnd":23,"startMs":1680,"endMs":2000}]}]},{"id":"penguin-learns-to-slide-p2","pageNo":2,"spread":"p2","imageUrl":"/seed/penguin-learns-to-slide/p2.webp","sentences":[{"id":"penguin-learns-to-slide-p2-s1","ord":0,"text":"Pip can walk, but he is slow.","translation_ko":"핍은 걸을 수 있지만 느려요.","audioUrl":"/seed/penguin-learns-to-slide/audio/p2-s1.mp3","wordTimings":[{"word":"Pip","charStart":0,"charEnd":3,"startMs":0,"endMs":320},{"word":"can","charStart":4,"charEnd":7,"startMs":320,"endMs":600},{"word":"walk","charStart":8,"charEnd":12,"startMs":600,"endMs":900},{"word":"but","charStart":14,"charEnd":17,"startMs":1120,"endMs":1460},{"word":"he","charStart":18,"charEnd":20,"startMs":1460,"endMs":1620},{"word":"is","charStart":21,"charEnd":23,"startMs":1620,"endMs":1860},{"word":"slow","charStart":24,"charEnd":28,"startMs":1860,"endMs":2120}]},{"id":"penguin-learns-to-slide-p2-s2","ord":1,"text":"He walks slowly up the hill.","translation_ko":"핍은 천천히 언덕을 올라가요.","audioUrl":"/seed/penguin-learns-to-slide/audio/p2-s2.mp3","wordTimings":[{"word":"He","charStart":0,"charEnd":2,"startMs":0,"endMs":220},{"word":"walks","charStart":3,"charEnd":8,"startMs":220,"endMs":580},{"word":"slowly","charStart":9,"charEnd":15,"startMs":580,"endMs":1020},{"word":"up","charStart":16,"charEnd":18,"startMs":1020,"endMs":1260},{"word":"the","charStart":19,"charEnd":22,"startMs":1260,"endMs":1640},{"word":"hill","charStart":23,"charEnd":27,"startMs":1640,"endMs":1680}]}]},{"id":"penguin-learns-to-slide-p3","pageNo":3,"spread":"p3","imageUrl":"/seed/penguin-learns-to-slide/p3.webp","sentences":[{"id":"penguin-learns-to-slide-p3-s1","ord":0,"text":"The hill is high and cold.","translation_ko":"언덕은 높고 추워요.","audioUrl":"/seed/penguin-learns-to-slide/audio/p3-s1.mp3","wordTimings":[{"word":"The","charStart":0,"charEnd":3,"startMs":0,"endMs":680},{"word":"hill","charStart":4,"charEnd":8,"startMs":680,"endMs":900},{"word":"is","charStart":9,"charEnd":11,"startMs":900,"endMs":1220},{"word":"high","charStart":12,"charEnd":16,"startMs":1220,"endMs":1540},{"word":"and","charStart":17,"charEnd":20,"startMs":1540,"endMs":1920},{"word":"cold","charStart":21,"charEnd":25,"startMs":1920,"endMs":2240}]},{"id":"penguin-learns-to-slide-p3-s2","ord":1,"text":"Then Pip falls down.","translation_ko":"그러다 핍이 넘어졌어요.","audioUrl":"/seed/penguin-learns-to-slide/audio/p3-s2.mp3","wordTimings":[{"word":"Then","charStart":0,"charEnd":4,"startMs":0,"endMs":580},{"word":"Pip","charStart":5,"charEnd":8,"startMs":580,"endMs":920},{"word":"falls","charStart":9,"charEnd":14,"startMs":920,"endMs":1540},{"word":"down","charStart":15,"charEnd":19,"startMs":1540,"endMs":1900}]}]},{"id":"penguin-learns-to-slide-p4","pageNo":4,"spread":"p4","imageUrl":"/seed/penguin-learns-to-slide/p4.webp","sentences":[{"id":"penguin-learns-to-slide-p4-s1","ord":0,"text":"A big friend comes to him.","translation_ko":"큰 친구가 핍에게 다가와요.","audioUrl":"/seed/penguin-learns-to-slide/audio/p4-s1.mp3","wordTimings":[{"word":"A","charStart":0,"charEnd":1,"startMs":0,"endMs":220},{"word":"big","charStart":2,"charEnd":5,"startMs":220,"endMs":580},{"word":"friend","charStart":6,"charEnd":12,"startMs":580,"endMs":860},{"word":"comes","charStart":13,"charEnd":18,"startMs":860,"endMs":1280},{"word":"to","charStart":19,"charEnd":21,"startMs":1280,"endMs":1460},{"word":"him","charStart":22,"charEnd":25,"startMs":1460,"endMs":1680}]},{"id":"penguin-learns-to-slide-p4-s2","ord":1,"text":"\"Watch me!\" she says.","translation_ko":"\"나를 봐!\" 친구가 말해요.","audioUrl":"/seed/penguin-learns-to-slide/audio/p4-s2.mp3","wordTimings":[{"word":"Watch","charStart":1,"charEnd":6,"startMs":0,"endMs":380},{"word":"me","charStart":7,"charEnd":9,"startMs":380,"endMs":680},{"word":"she","charStart":12,"charEnd":15,"startMs":1100,"endMs":1240},{"word":"says","charStart":16,"charEnd":20,"startMs":1240,"endMs":1560}]}]},{"id":"penguin-learns-to-slide-p5","pageNo":5,"spread":"p5","imageUrl":"/seed/penguin-learns-to-slide/p5.webp","sentences":[{"id":"penguin-learns-to-slide-p5-s1","ord":0,"text":"She lies on her belly.","translation_ko":"친구가 배를 깔고 누워요.","audioUrl":"/seed/penguin-learns-to-slide/audio/p5-s1.mp3","wordTimings":[{"word":"She","charStart":0,"charEnd":3,"startMs":0,"endMs":400},{"word":"lies","charStart":4,"charEnd":8,"startMs":400,"endMs":780},{"word":"on","charStart":9,"charEnd":11,"startMs":780,"endMs":1020},{"word":"her","charStart":12,"charEnd":15,"startMs":1020,"endMs":1220},{"word":"belly","charStart":16,"charEnd":21,"startMs":1220,"endMs":1400}]},{"id":"penguin-learns-to-slide-p5-s2","ord":1,"text":"She slides down fast.","translation_ko":"친구가 빠르게 미끄러져 내려가요.","audioUrl":"/seed/penguin-learns-to-slide/audio/p5-s2.mp3","wordTimings":[{"word":"She","charStart":0,"charEnd":3,"startMs":0,"endMs":680},{"word":"slides","charStart":4,"charEnd":10,"startMs":680,"endMs":1020},{"word":"down","charStart":11,"charEnd":15,"startMs":1020,"endMs":1420},{"word":"fast","charStart":16,"charEnd":20,"startMs":1420,"endMs":1800}]}]},{"id":"penguin-learns-to-slide-p6","pageNo":6,"spread":"p6","imageUrl":"/seed/penguin-learns-to-slide/p6.webp","sentences":[{"id":"penguin-learns-to-slide-p6-s1","ord":0,"text":"\"You can try too,\" she says.","translation_ko":"\"너도 해 볼 수 있어.\" 친구가 말해요.","audioUrl":"/seed/penguin-learns-to-slide/audio/p6-s1.mp3","wordTimings":[{"word":"You","charStart":1,"charEnd":4,"startMs":0,"endMs":300},{"word":"can","charStart":5,"charEnd":8,"startMs":300,"endMs":580},{"word":"try","charStart":9,"charEnd":12,"startMs":580,"endMs":820},{"word":"too","charStart":13,"charEnd":16,"startMs":820,"endMs":1260},{"word":"she","charStart":19,"charEnd":22,"startMs":1500,"endMs":1680},{"word":"says","charStart":23,"charEnd":27,"startMs":1680,"endMs":2020}]},{"id":"penguin-learns-to-slide-p6-s2","ord":1,"text":"Pip is afraid.","translation_ko":"핍은 무서워요.","audioUrl":"/seed/penguin-learns-to-slide/audio/p6-s2.mp3","wordTimings":[{"word":"Pip","charStart":0,"charEnd":3,"startMs":0,"endMs":660},{"word":"is","charStart":4,"charEnd":6,"startMs":660,"endMs":1100},{"word":"afraid","charStart":7,"charEnd":13,"startMs":1100,"endMs":1420}]}]},{"id":"penguin-learns-to-slide-p7","pageNo":7,"spread":"p7","imageUrl":"/seed/penguin-learns-to-slide/p7.webp","sentences":[{"id":"penguin-learns-to-slide-p7-s1","ord":0,"text":"Pip lies down and tries.","translation_ko":"핍이 누워서 해 봐요.","audioUrl":"/seed/penguin-learns-to-slide/audio/p7-s1.mp3","wordTimings":[{"word":"Pip","charStart":0,"charEnd":3,"startMs":0,"endMs":240},{"word":"lies","charStart":4,"charEnd":8,"startMs":240,"endMs":560},{"word":"down","charStart":9,"charEnd":13,"startMs":560,"endMs":940},{"word":"and","charStart":14,"charEnd":17,"startMs":940,"endMs":1160},{"word":"tries","charStart":18,"charEnd":23,"startMs":1160,"endMs":1520}]},{"id":"penguin-learns-to-slide-p7-s2","ord":1,"text":"But he stops too soon.","translation_ko":"하지만 너무 빨리 멈춰요.","audioUrl":"/seed/penguin-learns-to-slide/audio/p7-s2.mp3","wordTimings":[{"word":"But","charStart":0,"charEnd":3,"startMs":0,"endMs":300},{"word":"he","charStart":4,"charEnd":6,"startMs":300,"endMs":520},{"word":"stops","charStart":7,"charEnd":12,"startMs":520,"endMs":920},{"word":"too","charStart":13,"charEnd":16,"startMs":920,"endMs":1200},{"word":"soon","charStart":17,"charEnd":21,"startMs":1200,"endMs":1520}]}]},{"id":"penguin-learns-to-slide-p8","pageNo":8,"spread":"p8","imageUrl":"/seed/penguin-learns-to-slide/p8.webp","sentences":[{"id":"penguin-learns-to-slide-p8-s1","ord":0,"text":"\"Try again!\" his friend says.","translation_ko":"\"다시 해 봐!\" 친구가 말해요.","audioUrl":"/seed/penguin-learns-to-slide/audio/p8-s1.mp3","wordTimings":[{"word":"Try","charStart":1,"charEnd":4,"startMs":0,"endMs":660},{"word":"again","charStart":5,"charEnd":10,"startMs":660,"endMs":1080},{"word":"his","charStart":13,"charEnd":16,"startMs":1420,"endMs":1600},{"word":"friend","charStart":17,"charEnd":23,"startMs":1600,"endMs":1860},{"word":"says","charStart":24,"charEnd":28,"startMs":1860,"endMs":2200}]},{"id":"penguin-learns-to-slide-p8-s2","ord":1,"text":"So Pip slides down the hill.","translation_ko":"그래서 핍이 언덕을 미끄러져 내려가요.","audioUrl":"/seed/penguin-learns-to-slide/audio/p8-s2.mp3","wordTimings":[{"word":"So","charStart":0,"charEnd":2,"startMs":0,"endMs":500},{"word":"Pip","charStart":3,"charEnd":6,"startMs":500,"endMs":700},{"word":"slides","charStart":7,"charEnd":13,"startMs":700,"endMs":1180},{"word":"down","charStart":14,"charEnd":18,"startMs":1180,"endMs":1480},{"word":"the","charStart":19,"charEnd":22,"startMs":1480,"endMs":1800},{"word":"hill","charStart":23,"charEnd":27,"startMs":1800,"endMs":1840}]}]},{"id":"penguin-learns-to-slide-p9","pageNo":9,"spread":"p9","imageUrl":"/seed/penguin-learns-to-slide/p9.webp","sentences":[{"id":"penguin-learns-to-slide-p9-s1","ord":0,"text":"\"Wheee!\" Pip shouts.","translation_ko":"\"와아!\" 핍이 소리쳐요.","audioUrl":"/seed/penguin-learns-to-slide/audio/p9-s1.mp3","wordTimings":[{"word":"Wheee","charStart":1,"charEnd":6,"startMs":0,"endMs":920},{"word":"Pip","charStart":9,"charEnd":12,"startMs":940,"endMs":1500},{"word":"shouts","charStart":13,"charEnd":19,"startMs":1500,"endMs":1900}]},{"id":"penguin-learns-to-slide-p9-s2","ord":1,"text":"Now Pip loves to slide.","translation_ko":"이제 핍은 미끄럼 타기를 좋아해요.","audioUrl":"/seed/penguin-learns-to-slide/audio/p9-s2.mp3","wordTimings":[{"word":"Now","charStart":0,"charEnd":3,"startMs":0,"endMs":540},{"word":"Pip","charStart":4,"charEnd":7,"startMs":1040,"endMs":1120},{"word":"loves","charStart":8,"charEnd":13,"startMs":1120,"endMs":1620},{"word":"to","charStart":14,"charEnd":16,"startMs":1620,"endMs":1940},{"word":"slide","charStart":17,"charEnd":22,"startMs":1940,"endMs":2200}]}]}],"quiz":[{"question_ko":"핍은 무엇을 좋아하나요?","type":"mc","options":["하얀 눈","파란 바다","초록 풀","노란 모래"],"answerIndex":0,"explain_ko":"핍은 하얀 눈을 좋아한다고 나와요.","id":"penguin-learns-to-slide-q1","ord":0},{"question_ko":"핍이 언덕에서 처음에 어떻게 되었나요?","type":"mc","options":["넘어졌어요","노래했어요","잠들었어요","헤엄쳤어요"],"answerIndex":0,"explain_ko":"언덕에서 핍은 넘어졌어요.","id":"penguin-learns-to-slide-q2","ord":1},{"question_ko":"큰 친구는 어떻게 미끄러져 내려갔나요?","type":"mc","options":["날아서","배를 깔고","굴러서","발로 서서"],"answerIndex":1,"explain_ko":"친구는 배를 깔고 누워서 미끄러졌어요.","id":"penguin-learns-to-slide-q3","ord":2},{"question_ko":"핍이 너무 빨리 멈춘 뒤, 친구가 뭐라고 했나요?","type":"mc","options":["집에 가라고","잠을 자라고","다시 해 보라고","그만하라고"],"answerIndex":2,"explain_ko":"친구는 \"다시 해 봐!\"라고 응원해 주었어요.","id":"penguin-learns-to-slide-q4","ord":3},{"question_ko":"이 이야기가 우리에게 알려 주는 것은 무엇인가요?","type":"mc","options":["혼자 노는 게 좋아요","눈은 위험해요","포기하지 않고 다시 하면 즐거워져요","친구는 멀리해야 해요"],"answerIndex":2,"explain_ko":"핍은 무서웠지만 다시 도전해서 미끄럼 타기를 좋아하게 되었어요.","id":"penguin-learns-to-slide-q5","ord":4}]}